Joanne Baron https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joanne_Baron 0 Joanne Baron (born February 3, 1953) is an American actress and Meisner Method acting coach. She was raised in Providence, Rhode Island and attended Classical and Pawtucket High Schools. She received early acceptance to the University of Connecticut, then pursued Broadway opportunities and sang in Reno Sweeny’s with Cissy Houston, Whitney Houston’s mother.
